<div id="review_3573414240" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3573414240" />
    <a title="Min (abookworld___)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/91563322-min-abookworld"><img alt="Min (abookworld___)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1598936689p2/91563322.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3573414240?book_show_action=true">Oct 03, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Min (abookworld___)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Min (abookworld___)" href="/user/show/91563322-min-abookworld">Min (abookworld___)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3573414240" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1044222264809131188">Thank you Toni for gifting me an e-arc copy of Broken Souls.<br/><br/>I really enjoyed this read as it has a perfect blend of mythology and urban fantasy. Written in both slow and intense pacing with interesting characters. <br/>It took me a few chapters to get into the story but overall I liked it.<br/>Full review on my blog. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


